Cyber Monday 2020 is here, and a number of South African retailers are running big specials on technology products. This follows after many local stores ran annual Black Friday specials over the past weekend, offering discounts across a variety of product categories. Due to the COVID-19 pandemic, however, many local retailers – especially those with brick-and-mortar stores – ran Black Friday specials over the entirety of November to accommodate social distancing and prevent the spread of the coronavirus. Many of these stores have continued their Black Friday or “Black November” sales over Cyber Monday, extending the duration of their specials. Major retailers which are offering big discounts on tech products include Takealot, Game, Incredible Connection, and Makro. We have listed some of the best tech deals you can get on Cyber Monday. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-378174" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-1-10-640x430.jpg" alt="Deals 1" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-1-10.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-1-10-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-1-10-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-378176" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-2-10-640x430.jpg" alt="Deals 2" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-2-10.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-2-10-595x400.jpg 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Deals-2-10-300x202.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-